<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset='utf-8'>
    <meta http-equiv='X-UA-Compatible' content='IE=edge'>
    <title>OldEcs - About</title>
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1'>
    <style>
        #lol {
            width: 400px;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #222;
            color: #fff;
        }
        
        .top-bar {
            background-color: #333;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            padding: 10px;
        }
        
        .top-bar-content {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #fff;
        }
        
        .nav {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .nav-item {
            margin-right: 10px;
        }
        
        .nav-item:last-child {
            margin-right: 0;
        }
        
        .nav-item a {
            text-decoration: none;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
        }
        
        .nav-item a:hover,
        .nav-item a.active {
            border-bottom: 2px solid #fff;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #333;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            margin-top: 50px;
        }
        
        h2 {
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .form-group input[type="text"],
        .form-group input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #fff;
            background-color: #444;
            color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        
        .form-group input[type="submit"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 10px;
            border: none;
            background-color: #555;
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .form-group input[type="submit"]:hover {
            background-color: #777;
        }
</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="top-bar">
        <div class="container top-bar-content">
            <div class="logo">OldEcs | Relive 2016</div>
            <div class="nav">
                <div class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/login">LOGIN</a>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/">SIGNUP</a>
                </div>
                <div class="nav-item">
                    <a href="/about" class="active">ABOUT</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="form-group">

    </div>
    <br>
    <h2>OldEcs is a 2016 revival, except this one is different than the rest. It has a completely custom ui.</h2>
    <h2>the client is also already done. This is made by, Life, Plastic, End and extendify_</h2>
</body>
</html>